OL,3,CMayor unveils first ever 'heat plan'
OL,4,Cto help Londoners during heatwaves
OL,6,FThe Mayor of London has unveiled the
OL,7,Fcapital's first ever heat plan to keep
OL,8,FLondoners safe during increasingly
OL,9,Ffrequent heatwaves.
OL,11,FExpanding access to public drinking
OL,12,Fwater and blue spaces are among the
OL,13,Fpriority areas of focus set out in the
OL,14,Fplan, entitled Heat Ready London.
OL,16,FSir Sadiq Khan said he hopes it will
OL,17,Fhelp tackle the "huge obstacles" the
OL,18,Fcity faces with rising temperatures.
OL,26,@yD@QOUyD@`O]
