PN,37202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782391699
OL,3,CMayor unveils first ever 'heat plan'
OL,4,Cto help Londoners during heatwaves
OL,6,FIt comes as the UK swelters in
OL,7,Fexceptional heat as the hottest ever
OL,8,FJune day was recorded, with
OL,9,Fprovisional temperatures reaching
OL,10,F36.1C in Gosport, Hampshire, on
OL,11,FWednesday.
OL,13,FHeat Ready London focuses on six key
OL,14,Fsectors: the built environment,
OL,15,Fbusiness and economy, emergency
OL,16,Fpreparedness, resilience and response,
OL,17,Fhealth and care, green space and
OL,18,Fnature and infrastructure.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782391699
OL,3,CMayor unveils first ever 'heat plan'
OL,4,Cto help Londoners during heatwaves
OL,6,FThe plan sets out a series of
OL,7,Fobjectives, which includes protecting
OL,8,FLondoners from the health impacts of
OL,9,Frising temperatures and prioritising
OL,10,Fvulnerable people in high-risk areas.
OL,12,FOther objectives include ensuring
OL,13,Fbuildings and green spaces are adapted
OL,14,Fto heat and provide shade, maintaining
OL,15,Fessential services and supporting
OL,16,Feconomic resilience.
OL,18,FSome 37 areas of focus are set out in
OL,19,Fthe report for the plan ` including
OL,20,Fexpanding access to cooling spaces and
OL,21,Fpublic drinking water.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782391699
OL,3,CMayor unveils first ever 'heat plan'
OL,4,Cto help Londoners during heatwaves
OL,6,FOther focus points include adapting
OL,7,Fthe highest risk homes to protect the
OL,8,Fvulnerable, expanding access to blue
OL,9,Fspaces, strengthening health and care
OL,10,Fsystem resilience and improving the
OL,11,Fresilience of critical infrastructure
OL,12,Fsuch as travel.
OL,14,FSir Sadiq said: "Rising temperatures
OL,15,Fare no longer a future threat ` they
OL,16,Fare becoming a growing reality for
OL,17,FLondoners.
OL,19,F"It is affecting our communities, from
OL,20,Fhomes and high streets to schools,
OL,21,Fhospitals and care services.
OL,26,@vD@QOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
