OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782391699
OL,3,CMayor unveils first ever 'heat plan'
OL,4,Cto help Londoners during heatwaves
OL,6,F"That is why I am proud to unveil Heat
OL,7,FReady London, London's first ever heat
OL,8,Fplan.
OL,10,F"This is a new vision that will help
OL,11,Ftackle the huge obstacles we face with
OL,12,Frising temperatures."
OL,14,FHe said the plan is "a call to action
OL,15,Fto our partners to use this framework
OL,16,Fto drive collective delivery so we can
OL,17,Fprotect lives and strengthen the
OL,18,Fresilience of our city".
OL,20,FSir Sadiq added: "We must act now.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUtD@UO]vD@UOUzD@WO]|D@ROU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
