OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782391699
OL,3,CMayor unveils first ever 'heat plan'
OL,4,Cto help Londoners during heatwaves
OL,6,F"By working in partnership, we can
OL,7,Fensure the benefits of climate action
OL,8,Fare shared by all Londoners and that
OL,9,Fthose who are most vulnerable are
OL,10,Fprotected as we build a greener and
OL,11,Ffairer London for everyone."
OL,13,FA study of London's 2022 heatwaves,
OL,14,Fwhich was used to form evidence for
OL,15,Fthe plan, found that the extreme
OL,16,Fweather that year cost the city #1.5
OL,17,Fbillion.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@\O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
