FL,373,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782391699
OL,3,CMayor unveils first ever 'heat plan'
OL,4,Cto help Londoners during heatwaves
OL,6,F"Responding to this challenge requires
OL,7,Fa joint effort from the public and
OL,8,Forganisations across London, including
OL,9,Ftaking steps in advance to prevent or
OL,10,Fminimise the harm and damage caused."
OL,12,FThe plan has been launched during
OL,13,FLondon Climate Action Week, which is
OL,14,Fsaid to be the largest independent
OL,15,Fclimate event in Europe.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
