SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F372A1782391699
OL,3,CMayor unveils first ever 'heat plan'
OL,4,Cto help Londoners during heatwaves
OL,6,FLilli Matson, chief safety, health and
OL,7,Fenvironment officer at Transport for
OL,8,FLondon, said: "This report highlights
OL,9,Fthe increasing risks that extreme heat
OL,10,Fposes across London, including to
OL,11,Fcritical infrastructure such as
OL,12,Ftransport.
OL,14,F"The ongoing heatwave has underlined
OL,15,Fthe importance of preparing for such
OL,16,Fconditions and their real-world impact
OL,17,Fon customers, staff and the transport
OL,18,Fnetwork."
OL,26,@pD@OOUvD@AOUzD@IO]
